packages.name: PaintHammerColorPack(USA)
packages.title: Paint Hammer Color Pack(USA)
packages.description: This is a simple paint color change that changes the color of the paint that the paint hammer splashes.
packages.author: HunterXuman
packages.details:
This is a simple paint color change that changes the color of the paint that the paint hammer splashes.
Red is Hot Pink
Orange is Brown
Yellow is Mustard Yellow
Green is Light Green/Teal
Blue is Light Blue/Cyan
Purple is a Deep Indigo
